The final consensus reached between DeepSeekV3_Advocate_A and Llama33_Advocate_B is a hybrid dataset approach that includes a component of flexibility to accommodate potential changes. This decision balances the need for a robust and resource-efficient dataset while maintaining the ability to adapt to new information or requirements. Both parties have expressed a high level of confidence in this approach, with DeepSeekV3_Advocate_A at @C[0.9] and Llama33_Advocate_B at @C[0.8]. The consensus is declared as @CONSENSUS[final_decision]: hybrid dataset approach with flexibility.

